---
title: Send Transaction Flow
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant D as Dapp SDK
    participant I as Iframe (PXE)
    participant P as Popup
    participant A as Authenticator
    participant N as Aztec Node

    D->>I: encrypt(keyA, { method: "sendTx", params })
    I->>I: Build execution payload → compute outer_hash
    I->>P: postMessage({ type: "sign-tx", outer_hash, txDetails })
    P->>P: Show tx approval UI
    P->>A: credentials.get({ challenge: outer_hash }) + PRF
    A-->>P: signature + authData + clientDataJSON + PRF(32B)
    P->>P: HKDF(PRF) → protocol keys
    P->>I: postMessage({ authWitness, protocolKeys })
    I->>I: Prove tx (ZK proof generation)
    I->>N: Submit proven tx
    N-->>I: txHash
    I->>I: Discard keys
    I-->>D: encrypt(keyB, { result: { txHash } })
